1Ô∏è‚É£ High-Level Architecture (HackerRank-style)
========================================================================================================================
Client (Web / Mobile)
        |
        |---- Username + Password
        |---- Google OAuth
        |---- GitHub OAuth
        |
Spring Boot Backend
        |
        |---- Spring Security
        |---- JWT Filter
        |---- OAuth2 Client
        |
Database (MySQL / PostgreSQL)
========================================================================================================================
2Ô∏è‚É£ Authentication Flow (Very Important)
========================================================================================================================
üîê Flow 1: Normal Login + JWT
========================================================================================================================
User ‚Üí /register ‚Üí save user (BCrypt password)
User ‚Üí /login ‚Üí authenticate ‚Üí generate JWT
Client ‚Üí sends JWT in Authorization header
========================================================================================================================
üîê Flow 2: OAuth Login (Google / GitHub)
========================================================================================================================
User ‚Üí Login with Google
Google ‚Üí Redirect to backend
Backend ‚Üí Verify user ‚Üí generate JWT
Frontend ‚Üí Store JWT ‚Üí use like normal login
OAuth is only for identity verification
JWT is still used for API security
========================================================================================================================
3Ô∏è‚É£ Tech Stack
========================================================================================================================
Layer	                                                    Tech
Backend	                                                Spring Boot 3
Security	                                            Spring Security 6
Auth	                                                JWT + OAuth2
DB	                                                    MySQL / PostgreSQL
ORM	                                                    Spring Data JPA
Password	                                            BCrypt
OAuth	                                                Google / GitHub
========================================================================================================================
